ivardefs.name: entry_
ivardefs.desc: An entry in a bundle resource - will either contain a resource, or information about a resource (transactions and history only).

ivardefs.name: identifier
ivardefs.desc: A persistent identifier for the batch that won't change as a batch is copied from server to server.

ivardefs.name: link_
ivardefs.desc: A series of links that provide context to this bundle.

ivardefs.name: signature
ivardefs.desc: Digital Signature - base64 encoded. XML-DSIg or a JWT.

ivardefs.name: total
ivardefs.desc: If a set of search matches, this is the total number of matches for the search (as opposed to the number of results in this bundle).

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the purpose of this bundle - how it was intended to be used.
